<h2 id="troubleshooting">6. Troubleshooting:</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Issue</strong>: Data Governance Platform fails to start.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution</strong>: Check Tomcat server logs for error messages. Verify database connectivity and configurations.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Issue</strong>: Data catalog is not displaying updated information.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution</strong>: Refresh metadata cache or trigger metadata synchronization process. Ensure data sources are accessible.</p>
<h2 id="faqs">7. FAQs:</h2>
<p><strong>Q1</strong>: Can the Data Governance Platform handle big data and streaming data sources?</p>
<p><strong>Answer</strong>: Yes, the platform supports integration with big data frameworks and streaming data platforms for comprehensive data governance.</p>
<p><strong>Q2</strong>: Is it possible to customize data governance policies and workflows?</p>
<p><strong>Answer</strong>: Absolutely, the platform offers extensive customization options for defining policies, workflows, and notifications based on organizational requirements.</p>
